  "Description": "PROCESSING:  This Job Loads Data from Sequential File created in xfrm Job and loads into IDS B_BCBSA_FEP_MBR_ENR table\n                                                                \n     \nMODIFICATIONS:\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                DATASTAGE               CODE                           DATE\nDEVELOPER             DATE                PROJECT                     DESCRIPTION                                                                                      ENVIRONMENT          REVIEWER                 REVIEW\n-----------------------------    ----------------------     ------------------------------        -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------  ------------------------------    ------------------------------       --------------------\nKalyan Neelam           2015-11-23        5403                              Initial Programming                                                                                IntegrateDev1           Bhoomi Dasari               11/27/2015\n\nAnnotations:\nRead Load File created in the FKEY job\nCopy Stage for buffer\nTruncate and Load B_BCBSA_FEP_MBR_ENR table\nLoad rejects are redirected into a Reject file"
}